{"tid":2090322,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"上肢極弱 求指點","createTime":"2020-07-02T05:55:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T11:52:19.000Z","uid":268642,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a8f11988750799a724a9bebc832f59020f124b06","tid":2090322,"uid":268642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:55:33.000Z","msg":"20 歲 63kg 175cm <br />\n<br />\n平時會行山 每日行1萬步左右 踢波可以夏天夜晚踢3 4 個鐘唔停都冇問題 <br />\n<br />\n最近的起心肝 襯summer 開始想操fit下  走左去跟nike 個training app 做左第一日咩 &quot;引爆燃點&quot;<br />\n<br />\n但係發現掌上壓淨係做到10下 隻手已經想斷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n做完10下 之後啲train 上肢既動作已經做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相反做下肢好輕鬆 完全冇壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n發現自己上肢係連最基本都達唔到 有冇巴打可以教下我有咩方法可以train 番隻上肢去合格水平<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nPlease Help!"},{"pid":"dcf0e157a85b49bb61f7e868021d19a673d4783a","tid":2090322,"uid":157901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"弱所以咪要操<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 三頭二頭操起"},{"pid":"c4dbe1d0c0fa27f7ae8946417e718ffb35f7856a","tid":2090322,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:59:35.000Z","msg":"我都係孱仔一個<br />\n我會答你由膝上壓操起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好怕柒 喺屋企做邊個知<br />\n由10*4咁開始做<br />\n每日/隔日做 每次做多少少 真係做唔到就抖多幾分鐘先做"},{"pid":"533bbffcac9fc3c49323a41b39524f0d71f303b6","tid":2090322,"uid":268642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c4dbe1d0c0fa27f7ae8946417e718ffb35f7856a","tid":2090322,"uid":26385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-02T05:59:35.000Z","msg":"我都係孱仔一個<br />\n我會答你由膝上壓操起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好怕柒 喺屋企做邊個知<br />\n由10*4咁開始做<br />\n每日/隔日做 每次做多少少 真係做唔到就抖多幾分鐘先做"},"citedB